-- Luis Morales <luis.morales@locationlabs.com> Tue, 02 Apr 2013 12:13:45 -0100

Package has been changed to depend on supervisor and no longer require the default-jre (openjdk) so you can use your
favorite flavor of java.

Agent configuration is placed in /etc/logstash/conf.d

The agent will read all config files located there


